ActCanadian Tourism Commission Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Industry of DRAGAN MATOVIC of Niagara Falls, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canadian Tourism Commission to hold office during pleasure on a part-time basis for a term of four years, in the place of Christiane Germain.
